<!doctype html>
<html lang="fr">
<head>
  <meta charset="utf-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1" />

  <style>
    .aurora-contact-component {
      --ink: #10201c;
      --muted: #5c6f68;
      --line: #dce8e3;
      --soft: #f3faf7;
      --primary: #0f766e;
      --primary-dark: #064e3b;
      --primary-soft: #e4f5f1;
      --white: #ffffff;

      font-family: Inter, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, "Segoe UI", sans-serif;
      color: var(--ink);
      background: #f7fbf9;
      border: 1px solid var(--line);
      border-radius: 12px;
      padding: 28px;
      overflow: hidden;
    }

    .aurora-contact-layout {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: 1.1fr 0.9fr;
      gap: 22px;
      align-items: stretch;
    }

    .aurora-contact-intro,
    .aurora-contact-card {
      background: var(--white);
      border: 1px solid var(--line);
      border-radius: 12px;
      padding: 24px;
      box-shadow: 0 10px 24px rgba(15, 118, 110, 0.06);
    }

    .aurora-contact-kicker {
      margin: 0 0 10px;
      color: var(--primary);
      font-size: 12px;
      font-weight: 800;
      letter-spacing: 0.14em;
      text-transform: uppercase;
    }

    .aurora-contact-intro h2 {
      margin: 0;
      color: var(--ink);
      font-size: clamp(26px, 3vw, 38px);
      line-height: 1.08;
    }

    .aurora-contact-intro p {
      margin: 14px 0 0;
      color: var(--muted);
      font-size: 15px;
      line-height: 1.65;
    }

    .aurora-contact-actions {
      display: flex;
      flex-wrap: wrap;
      gap: 10px;
      margin-top: 22px;
    }

    .aurora-contact-button {
      display: inline-flex;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: center;
      gap: 8px;
      border-radius: 8px;
      padding: 12px 15px;
      font-size: 14px;
      font-weight: 800;
      text-decoration: none;
      transition: 0.2s ease;
    }

    .aurora-contact-button-primary {
      border: 1px solid var(--primary);
      background: var(--primary);
      color: #fff;
    }

    .aurora-contact-button-primary:hover {
      background: var(--primary-dark);
      border-color: var(--primary-dark);
    }

    .aurora-contact-button-secondary {
      border: 1px solid #99d7ce;
      background: var(--primary-soft);
      color: var(--primary-dark);
    }

    .aurora-contact-button-secondary:hover {
      border-color: var(--primary);
      background: #d7f0eb;
    }

    .aurora-contact-note {
      margin-top: 20px;
      border-radius: 10px;
      background: var(--soft);
      padding: 14px;
      color: var(--muted);
      font-size: 13px;
      line-height: 1.55;
    }

    .aurora-contact-card h3 {
      margin: 0 0 16px;
      color: var(--ink);
      font-size: 20px;
      line-height: 1.25;
    }

    .aurora-contact-list {
      display: grid;
      gap: 12px;
    }

    .aurora-contact-item {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: 42px 1fr;
      gap: 12px;
      align-items: start;
      border: 1px solid var(--line);
      border-radius: 10px;
      background: #fff;
      padding: 14px;
    }

    .aurora-contact-icon {
      width: 42px;
      height: 42px;
      border-radius: 10px;
      background: var(--primary-soft);
      color: var(--primary-dark);
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: center;
      font-weight: 900;
      font-size: 18px;
    }

    .aurora-contact-item span {
      display: block;
      margin-bottom: 4px;
      color: var(--muted);
      font-size: 11px;
      font-weight: 800;
      letter-spacing: 0.12em;
      text-transform: uppercase;
    }

    .aurora-contact-item a,
    .aurora-contact-item strong {
      color: var(--ink);
      font-size: 14px;
      font-weight: 800;
      text-decoration: none;
      word-break: break-word;
    }

    .aurora-contact-item a:hover {
      color: var(--primary);
      text-decoration: underline;
    }

    .aurora-contact-footer {
      margin-top: 18px;
      border-top: 1px solid var(--line);
      padding-top: 14px;
      color: var(--muted);
      font-size: 13px;
      line-height: 1.55;
    }

    @media (max-width: 820px) {
      .aurora-contact-component {
        padding: 18px;
      }

      .aurora-contact-layout {
        grid-template-columns: 1fr;
      }

      .aurora-contact-intro,
      .aurora-contact-card {
        padding: 20px;
      }

      .aurora-contact-actions {
        flex-direction: column;
      }

      .aurora-contact-button {
        width: 100%;
        box-sizing: border-box;
      }
    }
  </style>
</head>

<body>
  <section class="aurora-contact-component">
    <div class="aurora-contact-layout">
      <div class="aurora-contact-intro">
        <p class="aurora-contact-kicker">Contact Aurora Cabinet</p>

        <h2>Échanger avec Aurora Cabinet</h2>

        <p>
          Vous souhaitez obtenir des informations, demander un devis ou planifier
          un échange concernant l’évaluation ESSMS ou la certification PSDM ?
          Contactez-nous directement par téléphone, par email ou en réservant
          un rendez-vous en ligne.
        </p>

        <div class="aurora-contact-actions">
          <a
            class="aurora-contact-button aurora-contact-button-primary"
            href="https://calendar.app.google/7jzdAA7uXkQoLcRu8"
            target="_blank"
            rel="noopener noreferrer"
          >
            Réserver un rendez-vous
          </a>

          <a
            class="aurora-contact-button aurora-contact-button-secondary"
            href="mailto:contact@aurora-cabinet.fr"
          >
            Envoyer un email
          </a>

          <a
            class="aurora-contact-button aurora-contact-button-secondary"
            href="tel:+33744473402"
          >
            Appeler Aurora Cabinet
          </a>
        </div>

        <div class="aurora-contact-note">
          Pour une demande de devis, vous pouvez préciser votre structure, votre
          activité, votre localisation, le périmètre concerné et l’échéance
          souhaitée. Cela permettra de vous répondre plus efficacement.
        </div>
      </div>

      <aside class="aurora-contact-card">
        <h3>Coordonnées</h3>

        <div class="aurora-contact-list">
          <div class="aurora-contact-item">
            <div class="aurora-contact-icon">✉</div>
            <div>
              <span>Email</span>
              <a href="mailto:contact@aurora-cabinet.fr">
                contact@aurora-cabinet.fr
              </a>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="aurora-contact-item">
            <div class="aurora-contact-icon">☎</div>
            <div>
              <span>Téléphone</span>
              <a href="tel:+33744473402">
                07 44 47 34 02
              </a>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="aurora-contact-item">
            <div class="aurora-contact-icon">◷</div>
            <div>
              <span>Rendez-vous</span>
              <a
                href="https://calendar.app.google/7jzdAA7uXkQoLcRu8"
                target="_blank"
                rel="noopener noreferrer"
              >
                Planifier un échange en visio
              </a>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="aurora-contact-item">
            <div class="aurora-contact-icon">⌂</div>
            <div>
              <span>Adresse</span>
              <strong>
                2 rue Gambetta<br />
                49400 Saumur
              </strong>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="aurora-contact-footer">
          Aurora Cabinet accompagne les structures dans leurs démarches
          d’évaluation ESSMS et dans le développement de son activité autour de
          la certification PSDM.
        </div>
      </aside>
    </div>
  </section>
</body>
</html>
